    a: 'English dominates (100%), but Malay and Chinese help reach government projects and property developers. Expand your reach.'
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I see examples?',
    a: 'Yes. We show you exactly what keywords we\'ll target. You approve before we start. No surprises.'
